        "Title": "Appropriate Consequences",
        "Location": "LOCATION_ROCKY_DUGONG",
        "PublicId": "134564652308",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Rocky/scene_dugong.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 527e339a-6320-4f7f-899c-22ed8da07de9).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47.\r\rA tourist named Mike took photographs of a pirate compound, intending to show them to his younger brother. A local woman reported him to the pirates. Later that day, four of them arrived and executed him on suspicion of being a reconnaissance agent.\rMike’s friend has contacted us and requested that those responsible face what they consider appropriate consequences.\r\rYou are to eliminate the four executioners, as well as the informant.\r\rWear something to blend in.\r\rGood hunting",
